	<div id="post-92589" class="post-92589 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-fin_anal_tec category-baudos-blog category-blog category-economia_finanza category-in-evidenza category-mercati entry">
		<div class="archive_postheader border_bottom_20">
			<h2 class="archive_title">
